  <summary date="2022-05-04T20:10:58Z" status="Introduced in House">Strategic Production Response Act

This bill limits the drawdown of petroleum in the Strategic Petroleum Reserve until the Department of Energy develops a plan to increase the percentage of federal lands leased for oil and gas production.</summary>
